# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Lock files we DO commit (kept here as documentation, not ignored):
#   - pyproject.toml (project + dev deps pinned by major)
#   - pip-resolved exact versions are recorded in docs/generalization/TECHNICAL_BASELINE.md
# We do NOT commit a uv.lock or poetry.lock in this bootstrap; pip is the
# reference installer for version 1.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
